  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0ddd\u0da8\u0dcf\u0db7\u0dba\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0d82\u0d9c\u0db4\u0dca\u0db4\u0dd6\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dda \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0db3\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dbb\u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc3\u0dcf\u0daf\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc4\u0ddd \u0db8\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Gotabaya has no privilege or immunity in Singapore",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Singapore's Foreign Minister said yesterday that former President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa will not be granted any privilege or immunity in Singapore.",
        "\"Normally, the Singapore government does not grant privileges, immunity and hospitality to former heads of state or heads of state. Therefore, former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has not been given any privileges, immunity or hospitality,\" said Singapore Minister Vivian Balakrishnan.",
        "Vivian said this in response to a parliamentary question tabled by Labor MP Gerald Giam on the privileges, immunities and hospitality accorded to former heads of state or heads of government traveling and transiting through Singapore.",
        "Giam also asked whether public resources were used and whether former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa was given privileges, immunity and hospitality in Singapore.",
        "In his written response, Vivian clarified that Rajapaksa had not been granted \"any privilege, immunity or hospitality\".",
        "Home Affairs Minister K. Shanmugam said foreigners who have a valid travel document and meet the entry requirements will be allowed to enter Singapore.",
        "\"We also reserve the right to deny entry to a foreigner if we judge it to be in our national interest,\" he said."
      ],
